<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 04:09:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军：从黎巴嫩发射的无人机在拦截尝试失败后坠落在北部空旷地区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-live/idf-drone-fired-from-lebanon-fell-in-open-area-in-north-after-failed-interception-attempt/0000018f-f5d1-d190-af8f-fff30f860000</link><description>也门胡塞武装在突然镇压中拘留了 11 名联合国工作人员以及援助人员 ■ 中央司令部：我们摧毁了也门胡塞武装在红海上空发射的四架无人机和两枚反舰弹道导弹 ■ 白宫等待哈马斯对停火提议的官方回应 ■以色列国防军称，一名哈马斯安全机构负责人在拉法附近的袭击中丧生 ■ 以色列国防军袭击了近东救济工程处学校操场上的集装箱，称哈马斯将其用作“行动中心”</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 03:35:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-live/idf-drone-fired-from-lebanon-fell-in-open-area-in-north-after-failed-interception-attempt/0000018f-f5d1-d190-af8f-fff30f860000</guid></item><item><title>“你支持恐怖主义”：10 月 7 日事件后，犹太学校的以色列阿拉伯教师面临迫害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-arab-teachers-in-jewish-schools-face-persecution-in-wake-of-oct-7/0000018f-f4d7-d84e-adbf-f5df0fe90000</link><description>尽管与以色列社会有疏离感，并且在某些情况下，个人安全感下降，但犹太教育系统中的阿拉伯教师仍然相信自己有使命要完成</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 23:33:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-arab-teachers-in-jewish-schools-face-persecution-in-wake-of-oct-7/0000018f-f4d7-d84e-adbf-f5df0fe90000</guid></item><item><title>“10 月 7 日，哈马斯想要引发大屠杀”：诺贝尔奖获得者作家赫塔·穆勒的采访</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-wanted-to-evoke-the-shoah-an-interview-with-nobel-winning-author-herta-muller/0000018f-edf4-d3f3-a7ff-fff482590000</link><description>诺贝尔文学奖获得者赫塔·穆勒从未试图隐瞒家族的纳粹历史，也从未试图逃避她生活在独裁统治下的岁月。事实上，她利用自己的过去来表达对现在的批评以及对以色列未来的担忧</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 22:32:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-wanted-to-evoke-the-shoah-an-interview-with-nobel-winning-author-herta-muller/0000018f-edf4-d3f3-a7ff-fff482590000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列打击真主党，伊朗也会加入。那么美国就会被拖进去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/the-danger-of-israels-unwillingness-to-see-gaza-and-lebanon-as-communicating-vessels/0000018f-f2be-df2e-a5df-f6ff23480000</link><description>以色列不仅拒绝了华盛顿的“通讯船”理论，而且还为攻击真主党作为防御举措建立了一个合乎逻辑但危险且鲁莽的理由</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 19:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/the-danger-of-israels-unwillingness-to-see-gaza-and-lebanon-as-communicating-vessels/0000018f-f2be-df2e-a5df-f6ff23480000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的军事审查似乎是在保护内塔尼亚胡，而不是国家安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-military-censor-seems-to-be-protecting-netanyahu-not-national-security/0000018f-f381-d084-abef-f7c96c420000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 17:53:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-military-censor-seems-to-be-protecting-netanyahu-not-national-security/0000018f-f381-d084-abef-f7c96c420000</guid></item><item><title>联合国将以色列和哈马斯列入加沙战争期间伤害冲突地区儿童的国家“黑名单”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/un-adds-israel-to-blacklist-of-countries-that-harm-children-amid-gaza-war/0000018f-f37e-d084-abef-f77f242f0000</link><description>虽然将以色列列入名单并不立即构成制裁的理由，但人们担心这最终会导致针对该国的决定。一位外交消息人士告诉路透社，哈马斯和巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织也将被列入联合国黑名单</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 16:51:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/un-adds-israel-to-blacklist-of-countries-that-harm-children-amid-gaza-war/0000018f-f37e-d084-abef-f77f242f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 245 天：据报道卡塔尔威胁驱逐哈马斯领导人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-245-qatar-reportedly-threatens-to-deport-hamas-leaders/0000018f-f312-d630-a7af-fbbafa8e0000</link><description>据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 报道，卡塔尔威胁称，如果哈马斯拒绝当前停火提议，将驱逐哈马斯领导人 ■ 内塔尼亚胡政府表示，任命一个国家调查委员会对 10 月 7 日进行调查的“时机尚未成熟” ■ 战时内阁部长甘茨将宣布辞职内塔尼亚胡政府于周六晚发表的讲话 ■ 战争进入 245 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 16:42:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-245-qatar-reportedly-threatens-to-deport-hamas-leaders/0000018f-f312-d630-a7af-fbbafa8e0000</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，随着战争死亡人数上升，加沙妇女和儿童被杀的频率减少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/women-and-children-of-gaza-are-killed-less-frequently-as-wars-toll-rises-data-shows/0000018f-f343-d190-af8f-fff3b4420000</link><description>美联社对加沙卫生部数据的审查显示，以色列与哈马斯战争中死亡的巴勒斯坦妇女和儿童人数似乎已大幅下降，因为以色列因加沙空前的平民伤亡而受到国际社会的强烈批评</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 16:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/women-and-children-of-gaza-are-killed-less-frequently-as-wars-toll-rises-data-shows/0000018f-f343-d190-af8f-fff3b4420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列甘茨预计将于周六宣布从内塔尼亚胡政府辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/benny-gantz-expected-to-announce-resignation-from-the-government-on-saturday/0000018f-f2f2-d190-af8f-fff2b6b90000</link><description>甘茨几周前宣布，他打算退出内塔尼亚胡领导的政府，除非加沙战后治理计划在 6 月 8 日之前获得批准。他还希望在发出最后通牒时，人质协议谈判能够取得进展过期</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 14:21:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/benny-gantz-expected-to-announce-resignation-from-the-government-on-saturday/0000018f-f2f2-d190-af8f-fff2b6b90000</guid></item><item><title>“每个人都伤痕累累”：美国犹太夏令营如何准备与众不同的一年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-u-s-jewish-summer-camps-are-preparing-for-a-year-like-no-other/0000018f-edca-d5c6-a1cf-fdde30550000</link><description>随着以色列-加沙战争进入第九个月，数万名美国犹太孩子即将前往夏令营。三名阵营负责人告诉《国土报》，他们已准备好应对这一前所未有的挑战</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 14:12:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-u-s-jewish-summer-camps-are-preparing-for-a-year-like-no-other/0000018f-edca-d5c6-a1cf-fdde30550000</guid></item><item><title>居民想要离开，预备役军人从未想过他们会回来——穿越以色列废弃北部的旅程</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-journey-across-israels-abandoned-north/0000018f-f276-d3f3-a7ff-f27678760000</link><description>在真主党的炮火之间，只有加利利的军事哨所已经满员，压倒性的情绪是一种绝望</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 13:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-journey-across-israels-abandoned-north/0000018f-f276-d3f3-a7ff-f27678760000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫最阴沉的骄傲活动让加沙人质成为焦点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tel-avivs-most-somber-pride-event-put-gaza-hostages-center-stage/0000018f-f18a-d55d-a39f-fd8e280e0000</link><description>随着加沙战争愈演愈烈，另一项停火和人质协议似乎还很遥远，特拉维夫这个以一年一度的骄傲游行而闻名的城市，今年的活动专门关注人质家属的困境，强化了他们与亲人见面的要求。那些返回</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 09:27:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tel-avivs-most-somber-pride-event-put-gaza-hostages-center-stage/0000018f-f18a-d55d-a39f-fd8e280e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府回应总检察长：10月7日成立调查委员会时机尚不成熟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/ag-urges-netanyahu-to-set-up-commission-of-inquiry-into-gaza-war-to-counter-backlash/0000018f-f170-dbca-a99f-fbf609770000</link><description>总检察长的信警告内塔尼亚胡，逃避对以色列在加沙行动的适当调查可能会导致“国家利益”受到“重大损害”，因为该国在国际法庭上面临挑战</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:02:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/ag-urges-netanyahu-to-set-up-commission-of-inquiry-into-gaza-war-to-counter-backlash/0000018f-f170-dbca-a99f-fbf609770000</guid></item><item><title>“一旦我离开以色列国防军，我就感到自己微不足道。一周后我被征召去执行预备役任务”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-07/ty-article/.highlight/once-i-left-the-idf-i-felt-insignificant-a-week-later-i-was-called-up-for-reserve-duty/0000018f-f0af-dbca-a99f-fbff27ee0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：两个朋友正在规划他们的退伍生活，一位音乐家和舞蹈家解释了为什么跟随比领导更有意义</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-07/ty-article/.highlight/once-i-left-the-idf-i-felt-insignificant-a-week-later-i-was-called-up-for-reserve-duty/0000018f-f0af-dbca-a99f-fbff27ee0000</guid></item><item><title>全球对以色列的经济抵制获得关注，但政府没有答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-global-economic-boycott-of-israel-gains-traction-but-the-government-has-no-answers/0000018f-efc2-df2e-a5df-eff711a20000</link><description>世界正在对以色列在加沙战争中的行为失去耐心并采取措施——限制出口、取消专业会议、放弃计划中的商业交易等等。当地消费者将遭受损失</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-global-economic-boycott-of-israel-gains-traction-but-the-government-has-no-answers/0000018f-efc2-df2e-a5df-eff711a20000</guid></item><item><title>国际合法性的减弱、疲惫不堪的军队和黎巴嫩战争将把以色列推向边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/waning-intl-legitimacy-an-exhausted-army-and-war-in-lebanon-will-push-israel-to-the-edge/0000018f-ef1b-d3f3-a7ff-ff3b7db00000</link><description>与真主党的战争将是以色列后方的重大挑战：北部和中部的城市将面临前所未有的规模和火力威胁。 在加沙，哈马斯和以色列国防军之间的版本之战仍在继续，而且缺乏明确的目标正在影响疲惫的士兵 ■ 对于悲惨的以色列国防军首领赫茨尔·哈勒维来说，时间已经不多了</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/waning-intl-legitimacy-an-exhausted-army-and-war-in-lebanon-will-push-israel-to-the-edge/0000018f-ef1b-d3f3-a7ff-ff3b7db00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡使用并虐待了甘茨和艾森科特——但当他们离开后，他会想念他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-used-and-abused-gantz-and-eisenkot-but-hell-miss-them-when-theyre-gone/0000018f-ef1d-dff6-a9df-ef9f9adb0000</link><description>如果民族团结党兑现其巩固内塔尼亚胡联盟的威胁，他将失去保护他免受国外更大批评的防弹衣。 ■ 当总理在美国国会发表讲话时，他将重复他在 2015 年的赌博——并希望有不同的结果</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-used-and-abused-gantz-and-eisenkot-but-hell-miss-them-when-theyre-gone/0000018f-ef1d-dff6-a9df-ef9f9adb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在拉法附近杀死哈马斯高级官员；白宫等待哈马斯对停火协议的回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-live/biden-israel-listened-to-u-s-concerns-on-rafah-netanyahu-to-address-congress-on-july-24/0000018f-f079-de64-a98f-f2fff0700000</link><description>以色列国防军袭击了近东救济工程处学校操场上的集装箱，据称哈马斯将其用作“行动中心” ■ 中央司令部表示，美国在加沙重建了人道主义物资码头 ■ 美国官员表示，国务卿布林肯将于周一抵达以色列 ■美国国际开发署宣布为加沙巴勒斯坦人提供超过 9000 万美元的援助，用于提供住房、水、食品、环境卫生和个人卫生</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 02:24:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-live/biden-israel-listened-to-u-s-concerns-on-rafah-netanyahu-to-address-congress-on-july-24/0000018f-f079-de64-a98f-f2fff0700000</guid></item><item><title>对于越来越多的以色列青少年来说，英语是逃离当地现实的一个出口</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/blame-tiktok-and-youtube-why-more-and-more-israeli-teens-speak-english-among-themselves/0000018f-ef47-dff6-a9df-efd7c1c60000</link><description>他们花几个小时在 YouTube 和 TikTok 上观看美国内容，沉浸在书籍、游戏和与世界各地的人聊天的世界中，并且更喜欢与当地朋友说英语。这些以色列青少年正在逐渐摆脱希伯来语</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 22:36:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/blame-tiktok-and-youtube-why-more-and-more-israeli-teens-speak-english-among-themselves/0000018f-ef47-dff6-a9df-efd7c1c60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将于 7 月 24 日向美国国会发表讲话，比原定日期晚六周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/report-netanyahu-to-address-u-s-congress-on-july-24-six-weeks-after-intended-date/0000018f-ef9b-d3f3-a7ff-ffbbf3090000</link><description>尚不清楚美国总统乔·拜登是否会在城里，这可能会在两位领导人之间引发高度政治化的摊牌</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 22:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/report-netanyahu-to-address-u-s-congress-on-july-24-six-weeks-after-intended-date/0000018f-ef9b-d3f3-a7ff-ffbbf3090000</guid></item></channel></rss>